vote.title: An ordinance amending Ordinance No. 32037, previously approved on October 27, 2021, which abandoned portions of an alley, located near the intersection of Malcolm X Boulevard and Taylor Street to SL4 Deep Ellum, LP, Meghani Partnership, Inc., Radical Computing, lnc., TRW Realty Holdings, LLC and Travertine, LLC, by altering Section 11 to extend certain requirements’ timeline from twelve months to eighteen months - Revenue: General Fund $7,800.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
